| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3975 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 557df922-d726-56c2-a617-1f6ec1ada5e9"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
